<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA62">
<l>mīṉeṉṉuṅ kampil veṟiyeṉṉum veḷḷivēy</l>
<l>vāṉeṉṉuṅ kēṭilā vāṉkuṭaikku tāṉōr</l>
<l>maṇikkāmpu pōṉimirntu maṇṇaḷantā ṉaṅkaḷ</l>
<l>piṇikkām perumaruntu piṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who measured the earth stretching himself like a unique</l>
<l>sapphire shaft for the indestructible pure umbrella called sky,</l>
<l>with a silver cover called emptiness on spokes called stars,</l>
<l>afterwards he is the great remedy for our diseases.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
